":"2019-11-15T04:52:14.000Z","msg":"推 大家吾好有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63d3b7b8debbc0a5c1e6c603125d928018419c86","tid":1721052,"uid":134002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:39:15.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n開頭係腳生紅點 少少痕<br />\n<br />\n之後到手都開始有 越來越痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇完醫生話致敏源入左血 即係皮膚敏感<br />\n<br />\n食左藥一個禮拜都仲未好 晚宴都會痕醒<br />\n<br />\n利申 無正面食過tg 但工作地區係tg旺區"},{"pid":"5dc935e499b3a24a77fb8a409206c790fe06d1a9","tid":1721052,"uid":134002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3dcc4c3e2fc7b8dfeda834af7a81a16207d51f02","tid":1721052,"uid":9412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:54:19.000Z","msg":"去若水忠醫（國難忠醫改咗名）到拎藥試下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:40:31.000Z","msg":"Telegram 問左症但未覆<br />\n邊到可以拎到藥？"},{"pid":"21fb6d7cbabd4d7c842dd46f3f6e5afd0663bae0","tid":1721052,"uid":187489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6373467938780a82eb7518c04a4bd9848d59c681","tid":1721052,"uid":53415,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:22:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:43:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}